title: Botched.S01E08.Silicone.Valley.WEB-DL.x264-RKSTR.mp4
description:
International singing sensation Monique's myriad of plastic surgeries have left her ears pulled down to her jawline. Can Drs. Dubrow and Nassif get her ear lobes fixed in time for her next music video shoot? Meanwhile, Kelly's childhood surgeries left her with a crooked nose and uneven lip. See if the corrective surgery finally gives her the confidence to take wedding photos she skipped years ago. Plus, Myesha's quest to be a model was halted by a cheap surgery that caused the bags under her eyes to swell. Watch her get back on track!

Many Thanks to Rockster again!!!
